# 2.20.2016

* `float: left` now only applies to columns within `.clearfix`.
* `.container` no longer extends `.clearfix`.
* `.row` will become deprecated in favor of the `.clearfix`.
* Introduced alternative shades to the main colors.
* Ratios are now fully configurable via a SASS map.

# 11.19.2016

* Moves breakpoint abbreviations to the front of class names (ie `md-wp-100`) to make it easier to scan mobile styles.
* Adds example settings and interaction settings files.
* Adds 0 to the position coordinates list. This gives us `.top-0`, `.left-0`, `.bottom-0`, and `.right-0`.

# 11.14.2016

* Adds `.origin-center` class for positioning elements by their center.

# 11.11.2016

* Changes how positioning classes are structured.
